Enroute to the Maldives 🏝️ with a layover in Instabul 🇹🇷 SAVE THIS TRAVEL HACK 👇🏼

Did you know that if you fly with @turkishairlines and have an international connecting flight in Istanbul and a layover between 6 and 24 hours, you can use their FREE „Touristanbul“ service to discover Istanbul? 🙌🏽😍 We had so much fun exploring this gorgeous city together with a really great guide 👍🏽 

Some of the stunning places we visited: 

- Hagia Sophia
- Basilica Cistern
- Blue Mosque
- Bosporus (we did a nice boat tour there)
- New Mosque
- Egyptian Bazaar
- Seven Hills Café
- Nova Santiye Café 

Btw trip will be very different than our other Maldives trips because we will also visit a local Maldivian island 😍 Thus we can show you that you can also visit the Maldives on a budget ☺️ In my Besties Group you can already find some first impressions ❤️

#touristanbul #turkishairlines #istanbul #turkey #turkiye #maldives #travelhack

Today we celebrate LOVE ❤️ This is our first & also our last Valentine‘s Day as fiancé & fiancée 🥹 Still feels unreal to write this and even crazier that next year we will celebrate as husband & wife 🥰

Whether you’re single, in a relationship or married we wish you the most beautiful day today filled with lots of love 🫶🏼 I‘m not only grateful for these two but also for you guys ❣️ Happy V-Day 🌹

Save these Top 10 AZORES TRAVEL TIPS 💚

1. Be prepared for everything - It‘s likely you will experience 4 seasons a day ⛈️
2. The hydrangea season in the Azores is from end of July to September - You might already see them earlier in the North East 🌸
3. There are 9 islands in the Azores - We absolutely loved visiting São Miguel & Flores 🇵🇹 
4. Swim under the waterfall „Cascata do Poço do Bacalhau“ 💦
5. Hike to „Miradouro da Grota do Inferno“ - ideally during sunset time 🌄
6. Do a boat trip to „Ilhéu de Vila Franca do Campo“ ⛵️ 
7. Explore the nature at „Miradouro da Ponta do Sossego“ 🌺
8. Book a whale watching tour - you will most likely also see dolphins 🐬 
9. Do the hike to the waterfalls „Poco da Ribeira do Ferreiro“ 👟
10. Visit the view point „Miradouro do Portal“ 🌊

Have you already been to the Azores or is it still on your bucket list? 🗺️

Tomorrow this little guy will turn 5 years old ✨ & I’m getting completely emotional every year around his Birthday 🥹

Usually we would always travel for his Birthday but this year we decided to stay home so he can celebrate with his friends 🫶🏼 Tomorrow we have planned a costume Birthday party for Mason with his besties 🥳 And on Monday he will have another Birthday celebration with his 15 kindergarten friends 🎂 #luckyboy

To be honest the past year has been my absolute favorite year with Mason ever 🥰 What was the favorite age of your kids? 🤍 I feel 4 & 5 are such rewarding and enjoyable ages, so I will definitely enjoy this year to the fullest 💕

#birthday #5yearsold #birthdayboy

Save this Bucket List Destination 🤍

Every year I try to visit some new countries or places I’ve never been to 🗺️ My trip to @visitsaudi has not only broadened my horizons, it has also helped me to foster strong connections and to deepen my cultural understanding 🔮 Also Messi is taking us in a journey to go beyond what we think about Saudi ☺️

I want to inspire you to embrace open-mindedness towards new cultures and destinations and to maintain an open heart while traveling 🫶🏼 By doing so we contribute to giving back tourism the power to act as a catalyst in building bridges between diverse cultures and societies, fostering understanding and mutual respect 🙏🏽

#ShareYourSaudi

Save this DIY Glazed Nail Inspo 🤍

Ich habe für die Anwendung die Nagelfolien @maniko.nails verwendet und gerade mal 10 Min. für diese wunderschöne Maniküre gebraucht 💅 

Mit meinem Code ➡️ MADELEINE_WINTER ⬅️ erhaltet ihr 20% Rabatt auf alles bei MANIKO 🙌🏽

Die Anwendung ist extrem easy: 
1. Nagelhaut zurückschieben
2. Nagel mit Alkoholtupfer reinigen 
3. Größe wählen 
4. Aufkleben und andrücken
5. Abfeilen 
6. 60 Sek. aushärten

Meine Nagelfolien, die ich hier verwendet habe, nennen sich übrigens „Glazed Sugar“ und gibt es auch als Pediküre-Set 🤍

Ich wünsche euch ein wunderschönes Wochenende ihr Lieben 😘
